Tigist Girma (amụrụ na 12 Julaị 1993) bụ onye Etiopia na-eme egwuregwu na-ahụ maka marathon.
Na Mee 1, 2021, Girma meriri na Ethiopian Olympic Marathon Trials na Sebeta City iji nweta ọnọdụ ya na 2020 Tokyo Olympics
Na 2:19:52 nke kachasi onwe ya MMA  site na Amsterdam Marathon na 2019 ma fọrọ nke nta ka ọ kwekọọ na Disemba 2020 na oge na Valencia Marathon nke 2:19:56.
